>  to redirect stdout to a file
>> to append stdout to a file
2> to redirct stderror to a file
2>> to append stderror to a file
&> to redirect both stdout and stderror to a file
sudo to run command as root


version.major.minor
version > breaking change
major   > new features
minor   > patches or bug fixes
uname => get info about the system
uname -r => get kernel version


lsblk to list your harddisk
lshw  to list all hardware
lscpu to list cpus
lsmem to list memory
dmsg to print kernel messages
